This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4373

Indenting for Shell script.

Indent levels at case labels keep the next line in the case line.
Or it can indenting using default shiftwidth. Please set the next line to vimrc.
let g:sh_indent_case_labels = 1

Consideration is kept for indent levels of inside the here document, when it is re-indent.
When here document finished, indent levels will be returned.
Also, indent levels of IFS is similar.
